41
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,820
This is way too dangerous.

42
00:05:32,290 --> 00:05:34,090
I don't want her to get involved.

43
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:36,760
But that doesn't mean you can
hide it from her.

44
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:37,760
What else can I do?

45
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,170
Tell her.

46
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,120
And make her worry about me?

47
00:05:43,140 --> 00:05:44,730
You think you're protecting her.

48
00:05:44,730 --> 00:05:46,220
You think she can't do anything.

49
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:47,550
Have you ever asked her?

50
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,400
Anyway, everything I did was

51
