Do you really think that's good for us?

216
00:18:29,610 --> 00:18:30,570
You're my bro.

217
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,340
Jiang Mu is my friend.

218
00:18:41,840 --> 00:18:44,040
I don't want you to follow my dad's path.

219
00:18:52,370 --> 00:18:53,240
I got it.

220
