257
00:21:17,520 --> 00:21:19,530
But when I arrived, I didn't see anyone.

258
00:21:19,530 --> 00:21:20,900
Master, I'm sorry.

259
00:21:20,930 --> 00:21:22,930
It was my fault for being negligent.

260
00:21:24,280 --> 00:21:26,100
